This is going to be a browser based mmo

The client will be built using htmx, being served using golang with echo


Mechanics

town, travel, dungeon crawling

technology required: 

procedural generation for terrain and poi(structures, towns, etc)

dungeons have tiers that dictate what monsters can spawn in them

professions:

    merchant:
        cannot go into dungeons, can set up shop and buy/sell items

    hunter:
        can hunt beasts and harvest resources

    adventurer:
        can go into dungeons, must buy gear from merchants

    craftsman:
        can produce items from resources

monster types:

    beast
    tier 1: deer
    tier 2: boar
    tier 3: wolf
    tier 4: bear